Package org.mule.extension.add2numbers.internal

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DemoConfiguration
    This class represents an extension configuration, values set in this class are commonly used across multiple operations since they represent something core from the extension.
    DemoConnection
    This class represents an extension connection just as example (there is no real connection with anything here c:).
    DemoConnectionProvider
    This class (as it's name implies) provides connection instances and the funcionality to disconnect and validate those connections.
    DemoExtension
    This is the main class of an extension, is the entry point from which configurations, connection providers, operations and sources are going to be declared.
    DemoOperations
    This class is a container for operations, every public method in this class will be taken as an extension operation.
